{"tid":2207080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國首相約翰遜：歡迎日本加入「五眼聯盟」","createTime":"2020-09-18T02:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T03:44:24.000Z","uid":53844,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"49334f7ad0fa6c4be3bd8c02275b46e1a073739a","tid":2207080,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-rfi-fr.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/s.rfi.fr/media/display/878319a0-f879-11ea-8ec3-005056a98db9/w:900/p:16x9/2020-09-16T165036Z_786995864_RC2SZI9K0DEX_RTRMADP_3_BRITAIN-POLITICS.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-rfi-fr.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F878319a0-f879-11ea-8ec3-005056a98db9%2Fw%3A900%2Fp%3A16x9%2F2020-09-16T165036Z_786995864_RC2SZI9K0DEX_RTRMADP_3_BRITAIN-POLITICS.JPG&h=584c6bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）9月16日就日本加入&ldquo;五眼聯盟&rdquo;情報分享體系的可能表示歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n日本前防衛大臣河野太郎曾於近期多次提及，日方有意加入這一情報互享的合作框架。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜當天在英國議會下議院接受議員質詢時提到了日本希望加入&ldquo;五眼聯盟&rdquo;一事。他表示，&ldquo;這是一個我們正在考慮的想法，但我們與日本擁有一個出色的關係，一個非常緊密的國防和安全夥伴關係&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n他說，&ldquo;這或許是一個（對&rdquo;五眼聯盟&ldquo;來說）很有效的擴展方式。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n他續指，&ldquo;對於英國來說，這確實是一個將志趣相投的民主國家帶到一起的巨大機會&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n他還介紹稱，目前尚未看到來自日方正式提出加入&ldquo;五眼聯盟&rdquo;的要求。<br />\n<br />\n東京方面，河野太郎上月在接受採訪時，表達了日方參與&ldquo;五眼聯盟&rdquo;的意願。他強調，&ldquo;我們是擁有共同價值觀的國家，日本幾乎可以稱得上是&lsquo;第六眼&rsquo;。<br />\n<br />\n另據了解，日本新任首相菅義偉已任命河野太郎為新的行政改革大臣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/20200917-%E8%8B%B1%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0%E9%81%9C-%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5-%E4%BA%94%E7%9C%BC%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F20200917-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%25B4%2584%25E7%25BF%25B0%25E9%2581%259C-%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%259C%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2580%25A7&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=f16f89a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://amp.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/20200917-%E8%8B%B1%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0%E9%81%9C-%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5-%E4%BA%94%E7%9C%BC%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7</a>"},{"pid":"231bb35f28fdaf0285f9f74783d35c7da786811c","tid":2207080,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9ccbc0babb301b942074475fd50c47b6ea1e4e","tid":2207080,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f528e4d801ea98b17b76b52351ef0e877b18bad5","tid":2207080,"uid":358542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"231bb35f28fdaf0285f9f74783d35c7da786811c","tid":2207080,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"點解咁愁？"},{"pid":"a478d1ff4362d4a5080cd052a56b36c88c25de1f","tid":2207080,"uid":178108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"中國：嬲"},{"pid":"9d2816f247101a5358f7a5463ec827ab85ce5d83","tid":2207080,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi